{"artefact":[["_response_info",{"status":"ok"}],["title","VAT registration thresholds"],["id","https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/vat-registration-thresholds.json"],["web_url","https://www.gov.uk/vat-registration-thresholds"],["format","answer"],["details",{"need_id":"B903","business_proposition":true,"alternative_title":"","overview":"VAT thresholds - VAT registration, Flat Rate Scheme, Cash Accounting Scheme or Annual Accounting Scheme","updated_at":"2012-10-02T12:14:40+00:00","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>The thresholds for registering for <abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> or joining a <abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> accounting scheme.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2><abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> thresholds</h2>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Circumstance</th>\n      <th>Threshold</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> <a href=\"/vat-registration\" title=\"VAT registration\">registration</a></td>\n      <td>\u00a377,000 or more</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Registration for <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/vat/managing/international/distance-selling.htm\" title=\"VAT and distance selling\">distance selling</a> into the UK</td>\n      <td>\u00a370,000 or more</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Registration for <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/vat/start/register/when-to-register.htm#3\" title=\"Acquisitions\">bringing goods into the UK from the EU</a> (known as &lsquo;acquisitions&rsquo;)</td>\n      <td>\u00a377,000 or more</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Completing <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/vat/managing/international/esl/reporting-esl.htm\" title=\"EC Sales List\">simplified EC Sales List</a></td>\n      <td>\u00a372,500 or less and supplies to EU countries \u00a310,000 or less</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h2><abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> accounting scheme thresholds</h2>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th><abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> accounting scheme</th>\n      <th>Threshold to join scheme</th>\n      <th>Threshold to leave scheme</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"/vat-flat-rate-scheme\" title=\"VAT Flat Rate Scheme\">Flat Rate Scheme</a></td>\n      <td>\u00a3150,000 or less</td>\n      <td>More than \u00a3230,000</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"/vat-cash-accounting-scheme\" title=\"VAT Cash Accounting Scheme\">Cash Accounting Scheme</a></td>\n      <td>\u00a31.35 million or less</td>\n      <td>More than \u00a31.6 million</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"/vat-annual-accounting-scheme\" title=\"VAT Annual Accounting Scheme\">Annual Accounting Scheme</a></td>\n      <td>\u00a31.35 million or less</td>\n      <td>More than \u00a31.6 million</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>There are different thresholds for other schemes like the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/vat/forms-rates/rates/rates-thresholds.htm\" title=\"Other VAT thresholds\"><abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> Retail schemes.</a></p>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice help-notice\">\n<p>The threshold is based on your <a href=\"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/vat/start/register/when-to-register.htm#6\" title=\"Calculate your VAT taxable turnover\" rel=\"external\"><abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> taxable turnover</a> - the total of everything sold that isn\u2019t <abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> exempt.</p>\n</div>\n\n"}],["tags",[{"title":"Business Link","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/businesslink.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":null,"type":"legacy_source"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=businesslink","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/businesslink"},"parent":null},{"title":"VAT","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/tax%2Fvat.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes returns online, rates, charging and record keeping","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=tax%2Fvat","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/tax/vat"},"parent":{"title":"Money and tax","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/tax.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes VAT, debt and inheritance tax","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=tax","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/tax"},"parent":null}}]],["related",[]]],"parts":null}